race.comment: BOUND'S MISSILE (1) has been in super consistent form recently with three minors on end before missing the frame latest finishing fifth (43.05) at Wentworth Park. Looks the one to beat on his best form. SECRET EMGRAND (2) has mixed form recently, finishing fifth (29.79) in a Grade 5 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. With a good start should be able to take advantage of the low draw. Can feature with the right run. JONESY REVENGE (8) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 5 lengths into second (30.69) at Taree Super Track in a Grade 5 over 525m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Expected to feature. TRUNKEY SHEARER (3) can play a role in the finish without surprising.
